  </header>

  <section class="card mb-10">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Service-level agreements</h2>
    <ul class="list-check">
      <li><strong>Phone</strong> — answer within 3 rings; if missed, return call within 5 minutes.</li>
      <li><strong>LINE OA</strong> — first response ≤ 15 minutes during 06:00–22:00; overnight queue cleared by 07:30.</li>
      <li><strong>Email</strong> — acknowledgment within 2 business hours; final itinerary or alternate within 24 hours.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="card mb-10">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Booking workflow</h2>
    <ol class="ml-5 text-slate-300 list-decimal space-y-2">
      <li>Verify member status and remaining rounds ({{ site.membership.rounds }} annual quota) in portal.</li>
      <li>Check allocation calendar and partner blackout dates.</li>
      <li>Submit request via partner course channel, capture confirmation number.</li>
      <li>Send itinerary (PDF + .ics) to executives and assistants; update ledger.</li>
      <li>Set cancellation reminder {{ site.membership.cancelHrs }} hours prior.</li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section class="card mb-10">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Escalations</h2>
    <ul class="list-check">
      <li><strong>Course overbooking</strong> — escalate to Partnerships Lead within 10 minutes; propose alternate of equal calibre.</li>
      <li><strong>Weather</strong> — monitor Thai Meteorological Department; pre-emptively contact members if storms forecast.</li>
      <li><strong>Hospitality incidents</strong> — log in incident tracker and inform General Manager immediately.</li>
    </ul>
